Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, this is the convent where it happened.}{\i0}Đây là nơi xảy ra vụ cháy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess...}{\i0}Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That guy... is the one I saw that day!}{\i0}Tên đó... là kẻ hôm trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I thought he had a keen interest in you!}{\i0}Mình cũng nghĩ hắn chú ý đến Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He wouldn't be a Yethma hunter, would he?}{\i0}Nhưng không lẽ lại là thợ săn?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um—}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{He looks like trouble.}{\i0}Một tên nguy hiểm!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig, what should we do?}Anh heo, phải làm sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Even if the three of us tried to take him on,\Nwe wouldn't stand a chance. For now, let's ju—}{\i0}Dù cả 3 chúng ta có\N lao lên cũng không thắng nổi, tóm lại--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Naut...}Anh Naut...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Good afternoon.}Chào buổi chiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Um, we don't need to worry\Nabout Mister Naut.}{\i0}Mọi người không cần lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What, you know him?}{\i0}Hả? Người quen sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Isn't he a Yethma hunter?}{\i0}Không phải thợ săn Yethma hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No, he's not.}{\i0}Không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's a very kind man.}{\i0}Là một người tốt bụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Please believe me.}{\i0}Hãy tin tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Oh, is that right? Very well, then!}{\i0}Vậy sao? Tôi đã hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Hold on a second, Jess!}{\i0}Khoan đã Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{It's too soon to trust him!}{\i0}Còn quá sớm để tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, Ceres...}Này Ceres...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That one's a Yethma\Nheading for the royal capital, right?}Cô gái Yethma kia đang đến thủ đô nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Did you bring them here\Nfor some sightseeing?}Dẫn đến đây tham quan hay gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Uh, no.}À không...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't say sightseeing.}Không phải tham quan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'd like to lay some flowers here.}Tôi đến đặt hoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that your idea of paying your respects?}Ra vẻ đồng cảm à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's all well and good, but...}Như vậy cũng được nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{that scarf... is a dead giveaway\Nthat you're hiding your collar.}cái khăn đó, không thể nào giấu được đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Take it off.}Cởi ra đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Put this one on.}Sử dụng cái này.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{From afar, you can't tell it apart\Nfrom your skin.}Nhìn từ xa sẽ không biết được vì cùng màu da.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But... if someone sees it close-up,\Nwouldn't that give me away on the spot?}Nhưng nếu lại gần, họ cũng sẽ biết thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The point is that no one would be able\Nto tell at a glance from afar.}Quan trọng là quan sát từ xa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's not for your sake.}Không phải vì cô đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm telling you all this\Nbecause you could put Ceres in danger.}Mà còn cả vì Ceres cũng sẽ gặp nguy hiểm nếu đi cùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just do as I say\Nand put this one on instead.}Nghe lời tôi và đeo nó vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{All right.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't let your guard down, Jess!}{\i0}Đừng bất cẩn, Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What are you, an adolescent?}{\i0}Này này, ngại cái quái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jeez!}{\i0}Thiệt tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Falling madly in love\Nwith a girl you just met...}{\i0}Vừa gặp gái đã đổ là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh well...}{\i0}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but at least he doesn't\Nseem all that dangerous.}{\i0}ít nhất hắn cũng không có gì nguy hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm going to keep my true identity\Na secret for now.}{\i0}Từ giờ hãy giữ bí mật thân thế của tôi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The second you're in harm's way,\NI'll let him know.}{\i0}Ngay khi Jess gặp nguy hiểm tôi sẽ báo cho hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thấy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Understood.}{\i0}Đã rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Will you help us out, too, Cutie-pie Ceres?}{\i0}Cả bé Ceres nữa, hãy giúp bọn tôi nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Cutie-pie?}{\i0}Bé?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Once I get the feeling that I can trust him,\NI'll let him know who I am right away.}{\i0}Đến khi nào tin tưởng\N được thì tôi sẽ nói thật về bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, until then, Ceres, could you treat me\Nlike I'm just a random pig?}{\i0}Vậy nên đến khi đó cứ\N xem tôi như con heo bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If you put it that way...}{\i0}Nếu đã vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{then yes, understood.}{\i0}tôi đã rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This should do it.}Vậy là được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much.}Cảm ơn anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{By the way...}Với cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I still don't know your name.}Tên cô là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm Jess.}Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you.}Rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tôi vào bên trong được không?{Are we allowed to go inside?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Look what kind of shape it's in.}Nhìn không khác gì bên ngoài đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Feel free to go in.}Thích thì cứ vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much!}Cảm ơn rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Did that set your mind at ease?}Đã thấy ổn hơn chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Excuse me!}Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I was told that there's a spring\Nsomewhere in this area.}Tôi nghe nói gần đây có suối?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What, going swimming?}Muốn đi bơi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Just what do you have in mind?\NAre you some kind of scumbag?}{\i0}Mày mong chờ cái gì hả thằng rác rưởi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No.}À không.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I thought I'd wash Mister Pig.}Tôi định tắm cho chú heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's nearby. Come on.}Cũng gần đây tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Ah!}{\i0}A!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Ah!}{\i0}Á!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Ah! Thanks!}{\i0}Cảm ơn nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's my thanks to you.}{\i0}Là đáp lễ ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You kept on walking\Nthe whole time I was asleep.}{\i0}Anh luôn cõng tôi trên lưng khi tôi ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, it's a two-way street.}{\i0}Đôi bên cùng có lợi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I had no choice but to transport you\Nbecause I had to flee.}{\i0}Vì không còn lựa chọn nào nên mới nhờ anh cõng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But that wasn't the case with you.}{\i0}Nhưng anh thì khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You did it so that I could sleep—}{\i0}Anh có thể lợi dụng lúc tôi ngủ--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không có đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Am I, really?}{\i0}Thật sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I did it out of my desire\Nto be straddled by those soft thighs of yours.}{\i0}Tôi làm điều đó vì muốn\N được kẹp giữa cặp đùi của Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Okay, let's leave it at that, then.}{\i0}Vậy thì cứ để thế cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oink!}{\i0}Éc!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's wearing his heart on his sleeve.}{\i0}Đúng là tên đơn giản.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Can I get two beers?}Cho tôi 2 bia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Excuse me...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about money.}Không cần lo vụ tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll pay.}Tôi trả.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much.}Cảm ơn rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{won't that get you in trouble with Ceres?}có khiến Ceres giận không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Why would I get in trouble with her?}Mắc gì con bé phải giận?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, well, Naut!}Chà chà Naut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I didn't know you were here!}Đến đây khi nào thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey Grams, long time no see!}Bà già, lâu không gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{How's the hunting going?}Cuộc đi săn thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Did it go well?}Có ổn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's going great.}Suôn sẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sure I can deliver you\Nsome bear meat tomorrow.}Ngày mai sẽ có thịt gấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that right? That's our Naut!}Thế à? Không hổ danh là Naut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll make a stew\Nand serve it to you on the house!}Vậy thì phải làm nồi lẩu chiêu đãi chứ nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I can't wait.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then, do you think Jess can have\Nsome of that stew, too, Grams?}Với cả có thể cho Jess công việc gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu cũng phải hiểu chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I can't keep a Yethma on her way\Nto the royal capital here for long.}Ta không thể giữ một Yethma\N đang trên đường đến thủ đô quá lâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry...}Xin lỗi nhé...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{but I'm going to have Jess\Nleave tomorrow morning.}Sáng mai Jess sẽ rời khỏi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{You're fine with that, aren't you?}Như vậy ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll be leaving for the royal capital\Ntomorrow morning.}Sáng mai tôi sẽ lên đường đến thủ đô.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Naut, try to confine your hunting to beasts.}Naut, cố gắng hạn chế săn quái vật đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's no secret to me...}Cậu nghĩ gì trong đầu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{what you have in mind, you know.}ta đều biết hết đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{After all, she does look a little like her.}Vì con bé nhìn y chang cô ấy mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:09:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I thought the same\Nwhen I first met her myself.}Lúc đầu gặp ta còn tưởng nhìn lầm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, shut up.}Im đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just leave me alone.}Kệ tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you for waiting.}Cảm ơn vì đã chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Uh... Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{have never had alcohol before.}chưa từng uống bia bao giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{They've got good beer here.}Bia ở đây ngon lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If you don't like it, I'll drink it.}Nếu không uống thì tôi uống cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just try tasting it.}Thử 1 miếng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well then, if you insist.}Vậy thì tôi xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I-It's delicious!}N-Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Why did you kill that heckripon, Mister Naut?}Tại sao anh lại giết Heckripon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Heckripons... are creatures\Nthat I've decided to kill on sight.}Heckripon, tôi sẽ giết ngay khi thấy nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{They only bring misfortune.}Chúng chỉ mang đến vận xui.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Although it's only been in the last few years\Nthat people started saying that.}Dù tin đồn chỉ mới vài năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, thanks!}{\i0}Cảm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Sure, no problem.}{\i0}Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, Jess...}Này Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Is that pig your pet?}Con heo đó là vật nuôi của cô à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He's my friend!}Nó là bạn tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You take really great care of him.}Hãy chăm sóc nó kĩ vào nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Have you been caring for him for a long time?}Cô đã chăm sóc nó từ lâu rồi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No, not really a long time, but...}Không, không hẳn vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig is who I'm sharing my destiny with.}Chú heo này chia sẻ cùng vận mệnh với tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Destiny?}Vận mệnh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's right.}{\i0}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm Jess's partner.}{\i0}Mình là đồng đội của Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You could even say we're bound\Nby a common destiny.}{\i0}Có thể nói là những đồng đội chung số mệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, I need to concentrate\Non fulfilling that role.}{\i0}Vì thế mình phải tập trung hoàn thành vai trò đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It wouldn't do to meddle.}{\i0}Không có thời gian lo những chuyện khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, I'm sure those things happen.}Mà, cũng có người này người kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Among you Yethmas.}Trong số Yethma các cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, Jess, are you okay?}{\i0}Này Jess, ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, I'm fine!}{\i0}Không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I feel so good!}{\i0}Tôi thấy ổn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's not what I mean!}{\i0}Ý tôi không phải thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That man is taking you—}{\i0}Tên đó đang dẫn cô--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No need to worry.}{\i0}Không cần phải lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Mister Naut would never assault me.}{\i0}Anh ấy sẽ không làm gì tôi đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Really?}{\i0}Thật không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Could you come with me?}Cô đi cùng tôi nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you asleep?}Cô ngủ rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm not asleep.}Tôi không có ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey you, don't you get any funny ideas!}{\i0}Này này, đừng có giở trò đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey!}{\i0}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oink!}{\i0}Éc!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, Jess!}{\i0}Này Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngực...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,tôi xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I guess I'll hurl my whole body through it!}{\i0}Phải dùng hết sức nặng để phá thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Nope, nope, nope, nope!}{\i0}Không không không!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Mister Naut would never assault me."}{\i0}Anh Naut sẽ không làm gì tôi đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess clearly said that!}{\i0}Jess đã nói rõ ràng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{In that case, I'm...}{\i0}Nếu thế thì mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{just gonna trust...}{\i0}chỉ cần tin tưởng...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Jess.}{\i0}vào Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm a bad girl after all.}Quả nhiên mình là kẻ xấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't even have the right to do this.}Mình không được phép làm thế này...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm...}Mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{a bad Yethma.}là một Yethma xấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{Nearly All Handsome Guys are Scumbags}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No sign that anything's been done to her.}{\i0}Không có gì xảy ra cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Who's there?}{\i0}Kẻ nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Mister Pig...}{\i0}Anh heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Ceres?}{\i0}Ceres?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What are you doing here at this hour?}{\i0}Sao lại đến vào giờ này?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, what was it\Nyou wanted to consult me about?}{\i0}Muốn bàn bạc về vụ gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I want you to tell Mister Naut\Nwho you really are first thing in the morning.}Sáng mai tôi muốn anh \Nnói thật về bản thân cho anh Naut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Naut? Well, that shouldn't be a problem.}{\i0}Naut? À thì cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But do I need to make a point\Nof going to see him for that?}{\i0}Nhưng có cần phải mất công nói không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Early tomorrow morning, Mister Naut\Nwill come to see Miss Jess for sure.}Sáng sớm mai, anh Naut nhất định sẽ đi gặp Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Come to see her? What for?}{\i0}Gặp? Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What do you mean?}Tại sao á...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{In order to...}Vì...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, what's wrong?}{\i0}Này, sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry.}Tôi xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But... because Mister Naut...}Nhưng... vì anh Naut...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Because he cares for Miss Jess...}Anh ấy quan tâm đến Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh, right.}{\i0}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's right.}{\i0}Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This little girl...}{\i0}Cô bé này...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm 13 now.}Tôi đã 13 tuổi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Are you in love with Naut?}{\i0}Yêu Naut à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I know!}Tôi biết chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{As a Yethma...}Một Yethma...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{as a child, I have no right to feel this way!}một đứa con nít, không được có cảm xúc này!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But I don't want Mister Naut to go!}Nhưng tôi không muốn anh Naut đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What do you mean,\Nyou don't want him to go?}{\i0}Cô bé không muốn anh ấy rời khỏi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Naut...}Anh Naut...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{is planning to go to the\Nroyal capital with Miss Jess!}đang định đến thủ đô cùng Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh?}{\i0}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Naut is planning\Nto become Miss Jess's chabirone!}Anh ấy định trở thành Chabirone đi cùng Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Chabirone?}{\i0}Chabirone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's a tradition we have.}Là truyền thống của chúng tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{For a Yethma to reach the royal capital safely,\Nthere's a condition she must meet.}Để một Yethma đến\N được thủ đô, cần có một điều kiện.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{that's the presence\Nof a wise, brave companion.}có một người đồng hành dũng cảm và thông minh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{A chabirone.}Một Chabirone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But... they say that...}Nhưng... Chabirone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{chabirones always vanish\Nalong with the Yethmas!}chắc chắn sẽ bị xoá bỏ cùng với Yethma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Forever.}Mãi mãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I get it.}{\i0}Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You think Naut's planning\Nto become Jess's chabirone.}{\i0}Cô nghĩ Naut định trở thành Chabirone của Jess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's why... you don't want Mister Naut\Nto become her chabirone, either, do you, Mister Pig?}Anh... cũng không muốn Naut\N trở thành Chabirone của Jess mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{After all, you—}Vì anh--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey!}{\i0}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Because Mister Pig...}Vì anh heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{you're in love with Miss Jess!}yêu quý Jess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Love" is such a loaded word, you know.}{\i0}Yêu cũng chỉ là lời nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's complicated for us grown-ups.}{\i0}Thế giới người lớn phức tạp hơn nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Martha said that you've been serving here\Nsince about five years ago.}{\i0}Martha nói rằng cô bé đã phục ở đây 5 năm trước?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{So, you've probably spent a long time\Ngetting closer and closer to Naut, right?}{\i0}Vậy là cả hai đã ở cùng nhau rất lâu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I think that's great!}{\i0}Tôi nghĩ điều đó thật tuyệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I think it's a wonderful thing\Nand a love that deserves to be fulfilled.}{\i0}Một tình yêu xứng đáng được trọn vẹn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Doesn't your love deserve\Nto be fulfilled, Mister Pig?}Thế tình cảm của anh thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{No, it doesn't.}{\i0}Không được đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Why is that?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess and I have only just met.}{\i0}Cả hai chỉ vừa mới gặp nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She was kind to me...}{\i0}Cô ấy quá tốt với tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{so I spontaneously started\Nhaving feelings for her.}{\i0}thế nên tôi bắt đầu nảy sinh tình cảm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's all there is to it.}{\i0}Chỉ như vậy thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{As a lowly pig, it'd be too selfish\Nto want to make Jess mine.}{\i0}Là một con heo thấp kém, thật quá\N ích kỉ khi muốn biến Jess thành của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Jess is kind to everyone.}{\i0}Jess tốt bụng với mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She only opened up to Naut\Nbecause she's kind to everyone.}{\i0}Cô bé mở lòng với Naut vì Jess rất tốt bụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That kindness isn't something\Nthat's only meant for me.}{\i0}Lòng tốt đó không hướng về chỉ mình tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And that doesn't bother me\Nin the least anymore.}{\i0}Và nó không khiến tôi bận lòng nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I haven't been a virgin\Nfor 19 years for nothing.}{\i0}Tôi là trai tân 19 năm không phải là vì mình muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But Mister Pig...}Nhưng anh Heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{you don't want Mister Naut\Nto be her chabirone, do you?}anh không muốn anh Naut\N trở thành Chabirone của Jess mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Well...}{\i0}Chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{but...}{\i0}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but I couldn't interfere with Jess's journey\Njust because of my own feelings.}{\i0}Tôi không thể cản trở chuyến hành trình\Ncủa Jess chỉ vì cảm xúc cá nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't worry.}{\i0}Đừng lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm going to reveal who I am.}{\i0}Tôi sẽ nói rõ thân phận của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Are you?}Thật sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much.}Cảm ơn anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If you go through Miss Jess or me...}Nếu thông qua Jess hoặc tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{we can relay your words to Mister Naut.}chúng ta có thể cho anh Naut lắng nghe suy nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is that another Yethma skill?}{\i0}Kĩ năng của Yethma à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I see.}{\i0}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Like a router?}{\i0}Giống như router nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{no matter how many years I try...}dù có cố gắng bao nhiêu năm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't think I'll ever be\Na match for Miss Jess.}thì cũng không có cửa với Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Because not even a day\Nafter she first met him, Miss Jess...}Vì Jess chỉ mới gặp anh Naut có một ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I wouldn't say that!}{\i0}Đừng nói thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're a lovely girl, too, Ceres!}{\i0}Cô bé cũng dễ thương lắm mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You're really charming...}{\i0}Thực sự quyến rũ đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and if I were a human,\NI'd hold you tight in my arms!}{\i0}nếu là người thì tôi sẽ ôm cô bé ngay rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Do you like young girls, Mister Pig?}Anh thích gái trẻ đẹp hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Uh, that didn't come out right.}{\i0}À không, vừa rồi là độc thoại.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Pretend you didn't hear it.}{\i0}Xem như chưa nghe gì đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I know I'm no match for her...}Biết là không có cửa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{because Miss Jess looks like her.}vì Jess rất giống chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Looks like her? Like who?}{\i0}Giống ai cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well...}Chuyện đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{W-Wait!}{\i0}K-Không lẽ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Could it be the owner of that collar\Nhanging up on the wall?}{\i0}Là về chủ nhân chiếc vòng cổ ở quán?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're very perceptive,\Naren't you, Mister Pig?}Anh nhạy thật đó anh heo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Naut was in love\Nwith someone named Miss Eise...}Anh Naut đã từng yêu người tên Eise đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{who used to work at that inn.}lúc cô ấy làm việc ở quán.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Although that love was never fulfilled.}Tình yêu đó đã không trọn vẹn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Instead of going to the royal capital,\Nshe was living in the convent in Baptsaze, right?}{\i0}Thay vì đến thủ đô, cô ấy chọn\N sống ở tu viện Baptsaze nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{After the convent caught fire...}Sau khi tu viện cháy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Miss Eise was abducted\Nby the Yethma hunters and then killed.}Cô Eise đã bị lũ thợ săn Yethma bắt và bị giết.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then, Mister Naut went\Nafter the Yethma hunters...}Sau đó anh Naut bám theo lũ thợ săn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{and he got Miss Eise's collar back.}và lấy lại chiếc vòng cổ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{By any chance...}{\i0}Không lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{did a bunch of heckripons\Ngather or something before that incident?}{\i0}trước khi vụ cháy xảy ra, có xuất hiện Heckripon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And that's why everyone in the village\Ntreats them like bad omens...}{\i0}Thế nên dân làng coi nó như động vật xui xẻo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{and why Naut started\Nfeeling the urge to kill them?}{\i0}và cũng là lý do Naut căm thù chúng?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I think you're right about that.}Có lẽ là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Ceres, have you ever met Eise?}{\i0}Ceres, cô từng gặp Eise chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No. I've only seen a picture.}Chưa, tôi chỉ thấy qua ảnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Naut wears a glass pendant\Nthat has Miss Eise's image burned into it.}Anh Naut đeo dây chuyền có ảnh cô Eise bị đốt trên đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Talk about obsessed.}{\i0}Anh ta ám ảnh luôn à...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And...}Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Naut used Miss Eise's bones\Nfor part of the hilts of his twin swords.}Anh Naut sử dụng xương của cô Eise làm kiếm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{As long as Mister Naut's grudge lasts...}Chừng nào nỗi hận thù 10 năm trước vẫn còn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{those twin swords will be enveloped in flames,\Nand he'll continue to kill Yethma hunters.}thì thành kiếm đó vẫn sẽ \Nbao trùm trong ngọn lửa báo thù thợ săn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's why...}Thế nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{there's no room for me\Nto enter Mister Naut's heart.}tôi không có chỗ trong trái tim anh ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey, Ceres...}{\i0}Này Ceres...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes?}Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Will you wait for us in the dining room\Ntomorrow morning, too?}{\i0}Ngày mai chờ tôi ở phòng ăn được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I want you...}{\i0}Tôi muốn cô bé...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{to help me convince him!}{\i0}giúp tôi truyền lời cho anh ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Đã rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Of course I'll be happy to help.}Tôi rất vui được giúp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À này...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Pig...}Anh Heo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's morning.}Sáng rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Morning already, huh?}{\i0}Sáng rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{About last night...}Đêm qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}Chuyện là...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That was rude of me!}Tôi đã thất lễ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What do you mean?}{\i0}Chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{After dinner, I came back to my room\Nand fell asleep just like that.}Sau bữa tối, tôi về phòng và ngủ thiếp đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rồi bỏ rơi anh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{When you're being so kind\Nas to accompany me...}Anh đã đồng hành cùng tôi vậy mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry!}Rất xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Don't worry.}{\i0}Đừng lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You were tired, right?}{\i0}Cô đã rất mệt mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's understandable.}{\i0}Đành chịu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You are angry, aren't you?}Quả nhiên anh rất giận.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Why would I be angry?}{\i0}Tại sao tôi phải giận?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{As long as you got some rest,\Nthat's good enough for me.}{\i0}Miễn cô ngủ nghỉ đầy đủ là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How are you feeling?}{\i0}Cô thấy sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Are you in any pain somewhere?}{\i0}Có đau ở đâu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không sao cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I feel really great!}Rất khoẻ khoắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I see.}{\i0}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, let's have breakfast and get going.}{\i0}Vậy thì đi ăn sáng thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Achoo!}Hắt xì!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, good morning...}Chào buổi sáng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Naut.}Anh Naut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, Jess...}Nè Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I've been thinking.}Tôi đã suy nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And, uh...}Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{See, I think I'll go with—}Tôi nghĩ mình sẽ đi cùng--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Excuse me!}Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mister Naut...}Anh Naut...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I need to tell you something.}Em có chuyện muốn nói.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This pig...}Chú heo này...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{is a human!}là người!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{Oh, Ceres, are you bad\Nat making deals or what?}{\i0}Ceres, cô hơi kém trong việc giải thích à.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What about this pig?}Con heo này thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This pig that's accompanying Miss Jess...}Anh heo này đi cùng Jess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Inside, he's a human being!}Bên trong đó là con người.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Please talk.}{\i0}Xin hãy nói đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I'll relay it to him.}{\i0}Tôi sẽ chuyền lời.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Uh...}{\i0}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Good morning.}{\i0}Chào cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Was that you just now?}Vừa rồi là gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Oh yes, it was this pig.}{\i0}À ừ, là con heo này đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It seems sketchy!}Đáng ngờ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Let's see you jump!}Nhảy xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Well?}{\i0}Thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Now do you believe me?}{\i0}Giờ tin chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You... Since when have you—}Cậu... từ khi nào--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I've been watching you\Never since we met yesterday.}{\i0}Tôi đã luôn quan sát từ hôm qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:22:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I saw you make Jess drink alcohol\Nand go into her room.}{\i0}Cho Jess uống bia xong dẫn về phòng.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{- Why, you!\N- Excuse me!}Tại sao?\N Em!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Miss Jess already has someone\Nto be her chabirone.}Jess đã có chabirone của riêng mình.
